"bursae ligaments-abdomen perineum, external approach. this class includes one or more of 19 standard surgical interventions or procedures on component parts of the bursae and ligaments of the abdomen and perineum with external approach.  these surgical interventions or procedures are listed in the world health organizations international statistical classification of diseases and related health problems or icd-10 pcs under code 0m.. . "
"bursae ligaments-abdomen perineum, external approach. this class includes one or more of 19 standard surgical interventions or procedures on component parts of the bursae and ligaments of the abdomen and perineum with external approach.  these surgical interventions or procedures are listed in the world health organizations international statistical classification of diseases and related health problems or icd-10 pcs under code 0m.. release perineum bursa and ligament,  external approach. this classification denotes the group of activities that yields a surgical intervention or procedure to release perineum bursa and ligament,  external approach.this surgical intervention or procedure is listed in the world health organizations international statistical classification of diseases and related health problems or icd-10 as code 0mnkxzz. "

"

"
